_sText:
This is the second map i release, a awp-arnena map, gameplay is like a mix of sniping and paintball, its not rare that someone sneaks around to the other side with a knife and scares the hell out of some sniper. This is one of my older maps but its pretty good visually. Hope you all like this one, i know i did.

If you wish to run this map on a server, feel free to contact me at "johan16_g@hotmail.com" Mail or Msn.
